                  <div class="node odd full-node node-type-page" id="node-4">
                   <div class="inner">
                    <div class="content clearfix">
                     <h3 align="left" class="MsoNormal">
                      Message from Payroll Office Director
                     </h3>
                     <p>
                      Welcome to the Appalachian State University Payroll Department website. The Payroll Department is responsible for the administration of all ASU payrolls including tax reporting, web time entry, departmental time reporting, time approving, salary redistributions, salary overpayments, salary underpayments, as well as the many other facets of payroll accounting. We are here to assist you, the employee or prospective employee and provide you with information that will ensure accurate and timely salary payments each paycheck. We strive for quality customer satisfaction and welcome everyone to please feel free to contact us with any questions or concerns (828) 262-6422. We look forward to serving you in the future.
                      <strong>
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       Lori Cornell
                       <br/>
                       Payroll Director
                       <br/>
                       Appalachian State University
                      </strong>
                     </p>
                    </div>
                   </div>
